<eesti>Tegevusp&otilde;hise kuluarvestuse raames omistatakse tootmise &uuml;ldkulud (kaudkulud): </eesti>
<inglise>In activity based costing, indirectly attributable costs are allocated to: </inglise>
<eesti>I tegevustele; </eesti>
